WEBVTT

00:00:00.038 --> 00:00:03.833
You know that whole thing about drinking
eight glasses of water a day?

00:00:03.833 --> 00:00:06.836
Sorry to have to tell you this,
but it's a myth.

00:00:06.878 --> 00:00:08.713
It won't make your skin brighter,

00:00:08.755 --> 00:00:10.798
it won't make you feel clearheaded,

00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:12.717
it won't make you feel more energetic.

00:00:12.717 --> 00:00:16.054
It might, however,
make you have to pee a lot.

00:00:16.095 --> 00:00:17.180
(Music)

00:00:17.180 --> 00:00:18.848
[Body Stuff with Dr. Jen Gunter]

00:00:18.848 --> 00:00:19.974
(Music)

00:00:20.016 --> 00:00:23.561
Many people don't understand
the biology behind their bodies.

00:00:23.603 --> 00:00:25.730
There's a lot of misinformation out there.

00:00:25.772 --> 00:00:29.859
But the truth is that when you understand
how your systems function,

00:00:29.859 --> 00:00:31.944
you're able to make better decisions.